WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:01.566
You are coming back

2
00:00:01.566 --> 00:00:04.566
After graduation, I want to go back to China to see you for four years

3
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:06.166
You're finally coming back.

4
00:00:06.166 --> 00:00:07.566
Miss me!

5
00:00:07.566 --> 00:00:08.966
I miss you, too.

6
00:00:08.966 --> 00:00:10.566
Call me first when you get off the plane

7
00:00:10.566 --> 00:00:12.900
I'm going to be angry if I'm sneaking around again this time

8
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.333
I'm going to get ready first

9
00:00:14.333 --> 00:00:16.200
It's been four years since I surprised you

10
00:00:16.266 --> 00:00:18.600
I have not contacted Gu Sijun for 4 years

11
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.600
I don't know if he is married to Su Chang

12
00:00:21.733 --> 00:00:23.700
Why are you standing here alone in a daze?

13
00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:28.900
Where are you going after graduation?

14
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:30.066
I'm going back home.

15
00:00:30.166 --> 00:00:34.166
Return to China to open your own wedding design studio?

16
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.300
I remember that your wedding dress is very beautiful.

17
00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:38.333
That wedding dress

18
00:00:38.333 --> 00:00:40.666
I could have bought it for 3 times the price

19
00:00:40.666 --> 00:00:42.700
I don't know who is so stupid

20
00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:44.266
Why don't you speak?

21
00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:46.100
I came back just to see my friends

22
00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.500
No other arrangements were made

23
00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:48.900
How time flies!

24
00:00:48.900 --> 00:00:51.766
I was still married when I went abroad

25
00:00:51.766 --> 00:00:53.466
They're having babies now.

26
00:00:53.666 --> 00:00:54.900
Speaking of which

27
00:00:54.900 --> 00:00:58.366
You haven't had a boyfriend in four years of college

